title: The Razy People - Bedlam (1968/2001) [mp3@320]
description:
The Razy People - Bedlam (1968/2001)

Genre: Canada, Psychedelic Rock

This 1969 Canadian exploit psychedelic LP featured quite a bit of wild & skewed points of view on the events of its day, assembled in sound montages edited together in the "Revolution #9" vein & Canadian Dreamies style, with fuzz guitar & outlandish organ sounds; although the musicians are uncredited, it is believed to have been created by the mysterious Johnny Kitchen

Tracklist:

01. Parade At The Funny Farm (J.Kitchen)
02. Head Amusement (L.Preissman)

04. After Six (P.Werber)
05. The Truth (J.Millman)
06. Head Games And Other Assorted Crap (J.Millman)
07. Head Job (R.Morris)
08. Happy Academy (F.Morris)
09. Trans Luv Airlines (L.Preissman)
